Usage: ecoOaDesign [-help] <lib> <cell> <view> -ecoVerilogFile <input_fileName>
                   [-reportFile <output_fileName>] [-useGACells <string>] [-postMask  [-suffix <suffix_name>]]

-help                                  # Prints out the command usage
<lib>                                  # Specifies the OpenAccess library name
                                       # (string, required)
<cell>                                 # Specifies the OpenAccess cell name of
                                       # the top cell to import (string, required)
<view>                                 # Specifies OpenAccess view name to
                                       # import (string, required)
-ecoVerilogFile <input_fileName>       # Specifies a Verilog netlist
                                       # (string, required)
-postMask                              # Specifies the postmask option
                                       # (bool, optional)
-reportFile <output_fileName>          # Specifies a report file. Default:
                                       # eco.log (string, optional)
-suffix <suffix_name>                  # Specifies the suffix name for the the
                                       # spare cells Default: _SPARE
                                       # (string, optional)
-useGACells <string>                   # Specifies the GA core site
                                       # (string, optional)